Jarom covers approximately 59 years, from about 420",["span.small","B.C."],"to 361",["span.small","B.C."],"(see",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/enos/1.25"},"Enos 1:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jarom/1.13"},"Jarom 1:13"],"). It was written in the land of Nephi."]]]]]],"refs":null}
